      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW GERTRUDE (5) has been out of the placings at her last two outings but shapes well for this if she can recapture her dominant win a few runs back, getting around this track over 525m in 29.92. Hot win three back and looks the one to beat here. LAKEVIEW LYNETTE (4) is a talented dog who is a winner of eight races and filled a minor placing latest when third at Sandown (29.35). Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Will give a great sight again. MEPUNGA EXPRESS (3) goes very well at the course and distance with three wins and a placing from six starts. Scored by 0.09 length last time (29.68) in a Grade 4/5 over 515m at Sandown. Looks well placed here and among the chances. PAW QWAN (1) found the frame here last start and looks a top-three hope again.",
